{"tid":2363454,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：美取消交流限制後　國務院助卿會見台北駐美代表蕭美琴","createTime":"2021-01-12T08:11:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T09:45:57.000Z","uid":290404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c9396408cf453327a534e6d863496117c2dcad8d","tid":2363454,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院取消美台交流限制後，國務院政軍局助理國務卿庫珀星期一與<strong>台北駐美代表</strong>蕭美琴會面。這是蕭美琴去年上任以來，兩人第2次會面。<br />\n<br />\n會面閉門進行。蕭美琴尊重美方公告不對媒體開放為由，不願意對會面多做說明。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國駐荷蘭大使胡克斯特拉在使館，與台北駐當地代表陳欣新會面，並在社交平台發文形容創造歷史，同時附上3張會面的相片。<br />\n<br />\n陳欣新對台灣傳媒表示，胡克斯特拉對台灣非常友善，以行動顯示對台灣的支持及展現美台關係友好，2人針對荷蘭相關議題交換看法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569963-20210112.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569963-20210112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=917e9bb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569963-20210112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=279707ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569963-20210112.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a05f2ccf4f78297aade51fa7740cc258963c3fd9","tid":2363454,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76d72f85e70ff47d96c7505fd0be47637884409","tid":2363454,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a05f2ccf4f78297aade51fa7740cc258963c3fd9","tid":2363454,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T08:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"港台咁寫梗係國家同城市之間既交流啦，台北喎！"},{"pid":"a232d2500ac4ee331bfb6ffc05a4bad428ee5880","tid":2363454,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}